OL,3,CRevealed: 28 computers taken from
OL,4,CBelfast hospital
OL,6,FTwenty-eight computers containing the
OL,7,Frecords of thousands of patients have
OL,8,Fbeen stolen from a Belfast Hospital,
OL,9,FUTV can reveal.
OL,11,FThe computers were being used to train
OL,12,Fstaff on the new encompass system, a
OL,13,Fdigital healthcare record that is
OL,14,Fbeing rolled out across all health
OL,15,Ftrusts.
OL,17,FBelfast Health Trust said the missing
OL,18,Fappliances "cannot access any patient
OL,19,Frecords and no data breaches have been
OL,20,Fidentified."
