OL,6,FHowever, SDLP MLA Colin McGrath said
OL,7,Fthe theft has raised serious concerns
OL,8,Fover the health trust's security
OL,9,Fmeasures.
OL,11,FThe theft was reported to police on
OL,12,FMarch 5, but the PSNI said it is
OL,13,Fbelieved to have taken place "over a
OL,14,Fperiod of several months."
OL,16,FIn a statement Belfast Health Trust
OL,17,Fsaid it "can confirm that a number of
OL,18,FPCs which were held in reserve for
OL,19,Fadditional encompass training cannot
OL,20,Fbe located."
