OL,6,FThe Trust added: "This does not affect
OL,7,Fcurrent staff ability to effectively
OL,8,Fuse the encompass system however some
OL,9,Ftraining has had to be rescheduled.
OL,11,F"The missing appliances cannot access
OL,12,Fany patient records and no data
OL,13,Fbreaches have been identified."
OL,15,FThe PSNI said a report of theft from a
OL,16,Fhospital located on the Lisburn Road
OL,17,Fin Belfast was received on Wednesday,
OL,18,FMarch 5.
