OL,6,FA spokesperson added: "It was reported
OL,7,Fthat around 28 computer base units had
OL,8,Fbeen stolen. It is believed the units,
OL,9,Fas well as a number of power cables,
OL,10,Fwere taken over a period of several
OL,11,Fmonths."
OL,13,FThe PSNI said enquiries are continuing.
OL,15,FColin McGrath MLA, a member of
OL,16,FStormont's Health Committee said the
OL,17,FBelfast Trust needs to reassess its
OL,18,Fsecurity measures urgently.
