OL,6,F"One would expect Trusts to have
OL,7,Fsecurity at the centre of everything,
OL,8,Fthat they will be able to keep areas
OL,9,Fclosed off so people cannot access
OL,10,Fthem unless they need to," he said.
OL,12,F"The fact 30 computers have walked out
OL,13,Fthe door does not provide any comfort
OL,14,Fthat is the case.
OL,16,F"What will be next? Will it be
OL,17,Fpersonal belongings of patients,
OL,18,Fpersonal belongings of staff,
OL,19,Fmedication? We don't really have the
OL,20,Ffaith that Belfast Trust is on top of
OL,21,Fits security detail here."
